data.description: Nestled near Keystone Lake in a peaceful rural setting. This 2 bedroom, 1 bath home, located on a corner lot offers a serene escape from the bustle of city life. Enjoy the warm ambiance of the open concept with beamed ceilings and charming fireplace, Updates include kitchen with granite countertops and added storage, bathroom, light fixtures and ceiling fan. All appliances are newer and stay with home. This well-maintained property also featured a 12x20 shed.
